715862f-a.text:
Avenue A., east side, southward from a point to the north of E. 7th Street and showing prominently the S.E. corner of same. Loews Hollywood Theatre (movie) is in the middle of the 6th to 7th Street block front. At the extreme left appears a small portion of Tompkins Square.

March 24, 1938

P.L. Sperr
